- Stop me?

990
01:10:50,885 --> 01:10:53,948
Those snobs! Well, they won't.
They or anybody else.

991
01:10:54,688 --> 01:10:58,317
I put ten years in. I put in everything
I ever earned into those estates.

992
01:10:59,007 --> 01:11:00,556
I'm not going to lose them.

993
01:11:01,420 --> 01:11:02,992
I'll get the money somewhere.

994
01:11:03,380 --> 01:11:05,962
Well .. I hope you do.

995
01:11:06,760 --> 01:11:08,485
But I don't think you can.

996
01:11:12,485 --> 01:11:15,452
Well Miss Seals, let's have the
rest of the unfinished business.

997
01:11:15,921 --> 01:11:20,628
The Roma Cement Company called.
- Ignore it. We're not building anything.

998
01:11:21,481 --> 01:11:24,057
Mr Durrell called, and a Mr Wilson.

999
01:11:25,039 --> 01:11:28,095
And Miss Heath from the hospital.
She said it was urgent.

1000
01:11:30,665 --> 01:11:34,259
Yes, I guess that does come
under "unfinished business".

1001
