- Yes, I blame you.

1008
01:12:07,984 --> 01:12:11,170
Don't say that Don,
don't .. it's a jinx.

1009
01:12:11,523 --> 01:12:12,521
I warned you.

1010
01:12:12,994 --> 01:12:14,489
I can't help it. I can't!

1011
01:12:16,112 --> 01:12:18,457
You mean you can't help
being rotten and selfish.

1012
01:12:19,237 --> 01:12:23,706
You'd do anything to gain your own desire
and go on, leaving someone else to pay.

1013
01:12:24,391 --> 01:12:26,487
That's the jinx you put on people.

1014
01:12:28,611 --> 01:12:30,501
I was willing to sacrifice
my life for you.

1015
01:12:31,428 --> 01:12:33,059
Is that selfishness?

1016
01:12:33,541 --> 01:12:36,897
Yes, as you were afraid to risk losing
me by telling me you had a husband.

1017
01:12:37,156 --> 01:12:39,405
So, instead you lied and ruined me.

1018
01:12:40,113 --> 01:12:42,419
And your husband .. what
it's cost him to love you.

1019
01:12:42,919 --> 01:12:45,994
Why, you never paid for any happiness
in your whole life. You owe for it!

1020
01:12:46,240 --> 01:12:48,177
It cost everybody else but you.

1021
01:12:50,148 --> 01:12:51,815
I can't afford any more.

1022
01:12:52,871 --> 01:12:54,128
There's one thing I know.

1023
01:12:54,228 --> 01:12:57,032
If you're ever going to be anything <i>but
</i>a jinx, you'd better start paying off.

1024
01:12:57,132 --> 01:12:59,130
Because you're in debt
for the rest of your life.

